@Carreau In thinking about this more, I think it may make better sense to add a redirect for the index view, from baseProjectUrl, rather than introducing a second Url setting. It make sense to have "new", "open", "copy" all go to the same baseProjectUrl, rather than just changing the behavior of "open".

Basically, my alternative notebook manager UI leverages the existing iPython notebook manager HTTP interface to create, copy, rename notebooks, but just list notebooks differently. 

I updated my branch accordingly.
